<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>LionTech Tomcat Maven Server</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #15211c;
      background: #f3f7f4;
    }
    main {
      max-width: 920px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 72px 24px;
    }
    section {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #dbe5de;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(17, 48, 40, 0.08);
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 42px;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #5e6b64;
    }
    code {
      background: #edf4ef;
      padding: 4px 7px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <section>
    <h1>Tomcat and Maven Server</h1>
    <p>This server is managed by Ansible for LionTech Solutions. Apache Tomcat is running on port <code>{{ tomcat_port }}</code> and Maven is installed for Java build workloads.</p>
    <p>Deploy WAR files to this Tomcat host after building with Maven.</p>
  </section>
</main>
</body>
</html>
